Description: Visually-focused Wayland compositor
 A visually-focused desktop system designed around smooth animations,
 thoughtful gestures and careful attention to detail, inspired by familiar
 macOS interactions.
 .
 Otto is a Wayland compositor and stacking window manager, built in Rust
 on top of LayersEngine and uses Skia for rendering. Features include
 multi-workspace window management, application dock and switcher, exposé
 view, animated genie minimize effect, and screen sharing via PipeWire.
